WEBVTT

00:00:00.710 --> 00:00:01.969
Don Cheadle: Home.

00:00:01.993 --> 00:00:03.761
It's where we celebrate our triumphs,

00:00:03.785 --> 00:00:06.935
make our memories
and confront our challenges.

00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:09.441
And these days there are plenty of those.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:13.967
An historic pandemic, wildfires,
floods and hurricanes

00:00:13.991 --> 00:00:16.094
all threaten our basic safety.

00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:18.412
These challenges hit even harder

00:00:18.436 --> 00:00:21.956
in communities that have been cut out
of equal opportunities.

00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:25.621
In the US, unfair
and racist housing policies,

00:00:25.645 --> 00:00:26.936
called redlining,

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:31.723
have for decades forced Black, brown,
Indigenous and poor white families